    • Class us.hourgeon.jmessenger.Model.ChannelHistory extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • channelUUID

          java.util.UUID channelUUID
          The UUID of the Channel which activity is recorded in this history

        • messages

          java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentSkipListSet<E> messages
          The Message objects ordered list It is the essence of the ChannelHistory object : the sequence of these messages is what an history is about. The Vector class is used for thread safety.

        • timestamp

          java.time.ZonedDateTime timestamp
          Timestamp of the instant the history was generated. The History object is immutable, and it was a **snapshot** of the Channel's state at **one moment in time**.
